data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
If the NRI is 4 bits long The value range of the NRI is 0 to 15. MMECode is from 0 to 240.
If it is 5 bits long. The value range is 0 to 31. MMECode is from 0 to 248.
If it is 6 bits long. The value range of the NRI is 0 to 63. MMECode is from 0 to 252.
If it is 7 bits long. The value range of the NRI is 0 to 127. MMECode is from 0 to 254.
If it is 8 bits long. The value range of the NRI is 0 to 255. MMECode is from 0 to 255
